{"tid":2178172,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"電視櫃問題","createTime":"2020-08-28T08:15:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-28T11:24:28.000Z","uid":197457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"2cd1e7fa68bff2644a7867e0ef34e25399185f2b","tid":2178172,"uid":197457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T08:15:41.000Z","msg":"想問大家個電視櫃係點樣分配<br />\n又要擺soundbar, PS4 , 網上行D盒仔, router , <br />\n睇上網D 圖  個個屋企都好似冇呢D野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果俾你地設計 你地會點分配<br />\n點先可以做到收納  又可以用到D機器影響 但又可以做到簡約效果<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62bd6d3b9e678e50515d136f943882ba03f8175a","tid":2178172,"uid":142964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T08:26:42.000Z","msg":"而家興就咁一塊雲石/石材係地下，d機/router/ sound bar放係係面，tv掛牆冇櫃，或做全包櫃，但中間留空掛tv，線走櫃/牆身，經個底拉返出黎接返d器材。<br />\n<br />\n又或者tv 掛牆，下面只做一個懸空式矮身櫃，soundbar放櫃面，其他機仔router個d放櫃入面，同樣tv走線經牆身落櫃接d器材，我屋企而家就係咁。<br />\n<br />\n想要放下野就兩邊整d層架。"},{"pid":"f146ee362810f9777a668a8cd03197fdbaa9f10b","tid":2178172,"uid":154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T08:43:01.000Z","msg":"線入牆，電視櫃部分偷空，放曬d 機入去"},{"pid":"a438e10074531b51462a0f128ac8beb3d3051696","tid":2178172,"uid":197457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"62bd6d3b9e678e50515d136f943882ba03f8175a","tid":2178172,"uid":142964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T08:26:42.000Z","msg":"而家興就咁一塊雲石/石材係地下，d機/router/ sound bar放係係面，tv掛牆冇櫃，或做全包櫃，但中間留空掛tv，線走櫃/牆身，經個底拉返出黎接返d器材。<br />\n<br />\n又或者tv 掛牆，下面只做一個懸空式矮身櫃，soundbar放櫃面，其他機仔router個d放櫃入面，同樣tv走線經牆身落櫃接d器材，我屋企而家就係咁。<br />\n<br />\n想要放下野就兩邊整d層架。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T08:45:29.000Z","msg":"第一個唔係好明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgm